## Appendix B: Charter Approval Questions

### Executive Approval Questions
| Question                                                                   | BRD Section Reference | Purpose                | Expected Output              |
| -------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------- | ---------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Does this project align with our Q[X] Microsoft transformation priorities? | Strategic Alignment   | Validate strategic fit | Clear alignment confirmation |
| What are the consequences of not doing this project?                       | Business Case         | Understand urgency     | Risk-based justification     |
| Are the proposed success metrics achievable and measurable?                | Success Criteria      | Validate targets       | Realistic, measurable KPIs   |
| Do we have the right stakeholder commitment for success?                   | Stakeholder Analysis  | Ensure support         | Confirmed stakeholder buy-in |

### Financial Validation Questions
| Question                                                       | BRD Section Reference | Purpose                  | Expected Output                 |
| -------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------- | ------------------------ | ------------------------------- |
| How does the ROI calculation account for implementation costs? | Budget Summary        | Validate financial model | Complete cost-benefit analysis  |
| What are the ongoing operational costs post-implementation?    | Resource Requirements | Understand total cost    | Operational budget requirements |
| When will we see the first measurable business benefits?       | Timeline              | Cash flow planning       | Benefit realization timeline    |

### Scope Validation Questions
| Question                                                    | BRD Section Reference | Purpose                           | Expected Output             |
| ----------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------- | --------------------------------- | --------------------------- |
| Are there any critical dependencies missing from the scope? | Dependencies          | Complete scope definition         | Updated dependency list     |
| What happens if we remove the lowest priority scope items?  | Scope Definition      | Understand minimum viable product | Prioritized scope framework |
| How will scope changes be managed during execution?         | Change Management     | Control scope creep               | Change control process      |

